{"tid":2487093,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"真實身材曝光！「最美笑臉」罕見脫了　豐滿半球震撼全網","createTime":"2021-04-13T10:07:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T10:27:09.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec9d33737958121a14e9b03fd79eb59f825dcf2","tid":2487093,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T10:07:48.000Z","msg":"南韓才華洋溢的正妹DJ眾多，最近有一位DJ Sura，人氣直追韓國美女DJ Soda（黃素熙），因此被外界封為「韓國第二女DJ」，在網路上掀起一陣熱潮，不過DJ Sura不僅有美貌，音樂才華更是出眾，過去還榮獲「世界百大女DJ」33名，IG擁有48萬多人追蹤，近日她罕見曬出一張辣照，再度引發網友熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/18/2942472-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F18%2F2942472-PH.jpg&h=76c7a3df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲DJ Sura被封為「韓國第二女DJ」。（圖／翻攝自DJ Sura IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/13/3108841-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F13%2F3108841-PH.jpg&h=4801fe57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDJ Sura外貌亮眼，身材其實也非常性感惹火，去年她甚至紅到台灣來，被封「最美笑臉」，或許是不想要讓出色外型搶走音樂才華，DJ Sura收起性感好一陣子，直到最近因為要宣傳直播節目，才又PO出身穿紅色兩截式泳衣，趴在「紅唇」浮在水面上的照片，只見DJ Sura令人噴鼻血的身材，搭配燦爛笑容，網友看完瞬間融化，「你穿泳衣的時候看起來真漂亮」、「太辣了啦」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/13/3108842-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F13%2F3108842-PH.jpg&h=d1e39856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲DJ Sura為宣傳節目罕見脫了。（圖／翻攝自DJ Sura IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/13/3108843-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F13%2F3108843-PH.jpg&h=106d4796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實DJ Sura的身材一直非常「不科學」，當時DJ Sura分享一系列自己戶外運動的照片，畫面中她穿著桃紅色貼身運動服，露出纖細手臂，以及0贅肉的纖細蠻腰，上圍和臀部卻相當豐滿，不科學的S型曲線，有時也讓不少粉絲擔心起她的健康問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/18/2942503-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F18%2F2942503-PH.jpg&h=1e474c15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲DJ Sura四肢纖細，卻有著「超不科學」的S曲線身材。（圖／翻攝自DJ Sura IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/18/2942469-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F18%2F2942469-PH.jpg&h=ce4368f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59f747da2f4d541ca85072eabc9c4023db6d4ffe","tid":2487093,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T10:08:18.000Z","msg":"誇張..<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9cd61ae1196b21ffc3e00e916dc6f08e9d3568","tid":2487093,"uid":132713,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"當然不是科學<br />\n是醫學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef712144ee91e27891ada70f8b272d0ad587034e","tid":2487093,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c9cd61ae1196b21ffc3e00e916dc6f08e9d3568","tid":2487093,"uid":132713,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"當然不是科學<br />\n是醫學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T10:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549a9c7de65ece76bf072854c44879fc82552501","tid":2487093,"uid":378357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T10:10:46.000Z","msg":"樣衰都仲要加士多啤梨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown